data.description: Located in the desirable and gated community of Glenwood Village. Large, low-maintenance rear yard has an extended patio with pavers. Upgraded kitchen with beautiful granite counters and stainless steel appliances. This 2-story home offers 3-bedrooms upstairs with laundry room, 1-bedroom on ground level and 3/4 bathroom with shower. 12'x12' tile throughout living area and master bedroom. Attached garage has convenient direct access to home.
